Class ActivityLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • ActivityLogger

  • public class ActivityLogger
extends java.lang.Object
    Used to log activities such as exercise and sleep on the user's account. Each user has one ActivityLogger
    Version:
    1.0 (11/11/2016)
    Author:
    Ana J. Garcia
    See Also:
    User, Activity
